to read 30 on the page.

00:47:15.670 --> 00:47:19.560 align:middle line:84%
>>To read a poem
privately is a beautiful--

00:47:19.560 --> 00:47:22.040 align:middle line:84%
can be a devotional,
prayerful thing.

00:47:22.040 --> 00:47:24.870 align:middle line:84%
But to have the poem
fall on the drum

00:47:24.870 --> 00:47:27.500 align:middle line:90%
of the ear, that's different.

00:47:27.500 --> 00:47:29.900 align:middle line:84%
Etheridge Knight, the great
African-American poet,

00:47:29.900 --> 00:47:34.785 align:middle line:84%
used to say, the
words from my mouth

00:47:34.785 --> 00:47:37.330 align:middle line:84%
are beating on the
drum in your ear.

00:47:37.330 --> 00:47:38.770 align:middle line:90%
So don't think this is casual.

00:47:38.770 --> 00:47:51.610 align:middle line:90%


00:47:51.610 --> 00:47:55.960 align:middle line:84%
>>I don't know why he should
come back and be so prevalent

00:47:55.960 --> 00:47:59.830 align:middle line:90%
700 years from his lifetime.

00:47:59.830 --> 00:48:02.080 align:middle line:90%
It may be a simple thing.

00:48:02.080 --> 00:48:06.530 align:middle line:10%
It may be it's because he's
telling a truth that we

00:48:06.530 --> 00:48:08.020 align:middle line:10%
are ready to hear.

00:48:08.020 --> 00:48:12.300 align:middle line:84%
And he tells it so clearly
and with such gentleness

00:48:12.300 --> 00:48:17.240 align:middle line:84%
and with such elegant
images that we

00:48:17.240 --> 00:48:19.920 align:middle line:90%
delight to hear his stories.

00:48:19.920 --> 00:48:25.215 align:middle line:84%
>>When something is true, it
can live 700 years or more.

00:48:25.215 --> 00:48:30.360 align:middle line:10%
We read Homer or we read
people who are older than Rumi,

00:48:30.360 --> 00:48:37.940 align:middle line:10%
and their beauty is just as
new today as it was then.

00:48:37.940 --> 00:48:41.800 align:middle line:84%
>>We're hard to understand
for ordinary people.

00:48:41.800 --> 00:48:49.620 align:middle line:10%
But they can feel the smell, the
fragrance, or feel the touch.

00:48:49.620 --> 00:48:52.980 align:middle line:90%


00:48:52.980 --> 00:48:56.830 align:middle line:84%
Another saying that's a
connection with the soul.

00:48:56.830 --> 00:49:04.540 align:middle line:84%
Even 700 years later, they
can touch the human hearts.

00:49:04.540 --> 00:49:08.280 align:middle line:90%
And they do, and they will.

00:49:08.280 --> 00:49:10.070 align:middle line:90%
>>Rumi is like bread.

00:49:10.070 --> 00:49:13.130 align:middle line:84%
It's not like
caviar that you can

00:49:13.130 --> 00:49:16.590 align:middle line:84%
